{"tid":989992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一日第二宗】大埔富善邨鋁窗飛墜　警刑事調查隊跟進","createTime":"2019-01-21T09:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T09:26:22.000Z","uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22964d607a52f1f8d77a7485f31b377e6abca686","tid":989992,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:22:52.000Z","msg":"一日內發生兩宗高空墜窗事件。下午12時許，大埔富善邨善美樓一扇鋁窗從高處墜下，跌至大廈對開樹底石壆，幸無撃中途人。該鋁窗大小約半米乘一米，玻璃碎裂窗框變形，由保安架設欄杆圍封及報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場調查，案件列容許物件從高處墜下，交大埔警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190121/s00001/5b306caa0f540afab9041ad64256cc25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190121%2Fs00001%2F5b306caa0f540afab9041ad64256cc25.jpg&h=3d33ccab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今早10時許，尖沙嘴美麗華酒店一扇鋁窗疑因鬆脫從16樓飛墜，一名女途人被擊中頭部陷入昏迷，送院搶救不治。"},{"pid":"0678a4e86eaa9611514d8e3901196feb4cd39452","tid":989992,"uid":19557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:23:47.000Z","msg":"唔知點解次次跌窗都一定會接二連三 大家行返d 有瓦姐頭既地方好d"},{"pid":"bef3a95538f5112441aa9b2029da1b72799683a8","tid":989992,"uid":154212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"強制驗窗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78ad36f09a05c3bfd09208842efe9b6c9d8cb4d","tid":989992,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:24:48.000Z","msg":"以前住公屋D人成張梳化同麻將檯飛落街都唔使拉"},{"pid":"c3e7c0cc24d7f6a9d981feb5ce8acffe127eaf1a","tid":989992,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:24:49.000Z","msg":"拿拿拿 喂喂喂"},{"pid":"5145b2604f8113d93284c43159eb6de3fe1d4965","tid":989992,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:25:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ac6QhpT-6NE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dac6QhpT-6NE&d=w7%2FbDBVMSsXhjs7